content: Are there accents in the second "how are you" in greetings?

I like how the autoplay of the phrases runs in a loop. My priority is to get good at listening. Can we have the option to use the system text-to-speech, please? My text-to-speech sounds better than yours.
A wonderful additional resource for learning Spanish.
My Spanish speaking  friends from Latin America tell me that I have very good pronunciation I owe it to this app
This is good for very basic communication not 'Pro', lacks many common phrases and religious words or phrases.  It also should have an option for business words and phrases.
